             <path class="feather" d="M625.494 72.103l-9.707 23.067-3.102-20.82c-.265-3.17 1.716-3.237 2.443-3.832-.133-.463-1.124-.463-1.124-.463h-1.848c-.198-5.42 4.028-7.8 7.462-7.535 3.697.132 7.856 4.428 5.876 9.583">
             </path>
             <path class="feather" d="M635.338 84.167L615.86 97.584l9.177-21.348c2.775-6.742 9.245-5.42 11.556-2.842 2.51 2.51 3.235 7.6-1.255 10.773">
             </path>
             <path class="feather" d="M637.448 99.9h-22.515l18.29-12.756c4.49-2.975 9.244-.266 10.498 3.635 1.327 4.36-1.65 9.12-6.27 9.12">
             </path>
            </g>
           </svg>
           <div class="brand">
            <span class="hfs-i hfs-i-vertical-msnbc">
            </span>
           </div>
          </span>
         </a>
        </div>

                 <a class="bacon-cards-twobythree__button" data-test="button" href="https://www.msnbc.com/reidout">
                  VIEW
                 </a>
                </div>
               </div>
              </div>
             </div>
            </div>
